g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:43:08.000Z","msg":"人往往將成功歸於自己<br />\n將失敗歸於環境<br />\n<br />\n實際你成功失敗都係因為環境(運氣)"},{"pid":"53c7ac2f26384c40c34c884ac1c72ebd4016d762","tid":2388171,"uid":379666,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3864ecca3f1c798e5fad1db5a9b7d1b38f2beb9e","tid":2388171,"uid":149844,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T02:14:07.000Z","msg":"投資都可以拉去性別問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"根本冇人話女人唔識投資 佢自己歧視女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10d32cddbbc606aa8c1f827352877e658ce579d","tid":2388171,"uid":290944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:52:48.000Z","msg":"兩年，連比特幣一個牛熊circle都未經歷過的人都開始教班。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efedd4333386ae85e04786a424c841a91c77622c","tid":2388171,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:53:54.000Z","msg":"可以一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f54cde2adfa005738e5938b08d7a9f34b6280e1","tid":2388171,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"即係賺左幾多??"},{"pid":"5503da309fcaffc3d8f73a5b22ac9eb81d020011","tid":2388171,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:56:56.000Z","msg":"年中究竟有幾多柒頭比錢搵雜誌寫膳稿R水魚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個都講到自己成功人士"},{"pid":"b21998360103135082104c0f094c1af008034040","tid":2388171,"uid":88725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"太太<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奴才可以服侍你"},{"pid":"364c482d4bfcd8682d8dd3ea115464d096a81ace","tid":2388171,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b66b82033fed063e773e3b0500cb3abecaa3470","tid":2388171,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T02:07:33.000Z","msg":"踏入2021年，比特幣價格旋風式搶高，一舉上破3萬、4萬美元，最高見過4.2萬美元。一時間，人人都說要買比特幣。加密貨幣場外交易平台Coiner創辦人Priscilla，近月見盡不少新手盲毛式入市，甚至有人對比特幣零概念下all-in，「好多人講玩比特幣身家翻倍，不用上班啦，環遊世界。如果你真系覺得放錢進去，它就會自己生錢，那就好易出事的。」<br />\n<br />\n她又慨嘆，投資市場一般男性主導，於加入市場後不時面對男士質疑，「一個觀念植入他們腦裡面，一個女仔有錢去擁有一點東西，就一定不系靠自己能力，為什麼大家不可以平等地去看這件事？其實好多女仔都好有投資賺錢能力。」<br />\n<br />\n兩年前斥六位數買Bitcoin 賺第一桶金<br />\n<br />\nPriscilla去年中創辦Coiner，主要經營美元穩定幣USDT場外兌換。場外交易所老闆娘，加上有外號「太太」之稱，我們登門訪問前，還以為她是加密幣市場老手？豈料一見真人，是一名外表標緻的80後時代女性，「我未結婚的，太太這個名其實系我助手改的，感覺就如果未見過人的話，系不會好先入為主覺得你後生，不問你事或者覺得不可靠。」而事實上，她參與比特幣投資亦只有2年多，但此2年，足以改變一生。<br />\n<br />\n兩年多前，她不諳投資，亦不了解加密幣，結果純粹因為「朋友叫」，就投資六位數掃比特幣，「投資不止十幾萬呀，當時比特幣系3,000尾、4,000頭美金左右，之後升到6,000幾美金，朋友就同我講可以離場呀。」身家雖然輕鬆double，今日回想起來，她坦承自己當時「未求知，先投資」膽生毛，「真系一個狗屎運囉，那時好彩無出事，一出事的話就什麼都沒有了，打工一輩子........<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://min.news/economy/324b693b9c014fa5cd212ae6924bc96a.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmin.news%2Feconomy%2F324b693b9c014fa5cd212ae6924bc96a.html&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWh6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=3891c7ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://min.news/economy/324b693b9c014fa5cd212ae6924bc96a.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">廢話不多講，相：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sd3PCDn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsd3PCDn.png&h=58fcff61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddwJG42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddwJG42.png&h=df7efc2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQjrERH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQjrERH.png&h=e68c7279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYN5aYn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYN5aYn.png&h=a04e8df5&s={SIZE}\" />